title: Grading S-'s & S's
body: I just played an extremely good game of darius going 14-2-12 with 320 cs for a 55 minute game. & upon finishing the game I was graded an A+, I was wondering why wasnt this graded an S- or S due to the score along with the cs.

replies.body: 320 cs for a 55 minute game is pretty low. That would be the problem...
